 0\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[1m\u001b[31mE             assert 0 == 5\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[1m\u001b[31mE              +  where 0 = len([])\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[1m\u001b[31mE           assert False\u001b[0m\r\n"]
